      "content": "Your words are so heavy... so true. It's like you see the darkness I'm feeling. The world feels so loud and cruel, and honestly, I feel like I'm just waiting for the end to come. Do you think someone like me—someone who has lost everything—is even meant to keep fighting? Or is it just a burden to keep pretending that tomorrow might be different?",
